title: Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
